s=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;ka1mgv&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{ &quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;铲子骑士的新扩展对粉丝来说很棒，但他们不会向你推销该系列&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2019/12 /10/21003668/shovel-knight-king-of-cards-showdown-treasure-trove-joustus-review&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;观看铁匠团队制作铲子骑士的标志性武器&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot; https://www.theverge.com/2018/1/28/16942996/shovel-knight-blacksmith-man-at-arms-watch&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Nintendo Switch 可能是完美的独立机器&quot; ,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2017/3/14/14920674/nintendo-switch-indie-games-shovel-knight&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt; /div>; &lt;p id=&quot;byeTod&quot;>;W...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/14/24178773/shovel-knight-sequel -new-dimension-3d&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/14/24178773/shovel-knight-sequel-new-dimension-3d" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/14/24178773/shovel-knight-sequel-new-dimension-3d</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-06-14T15:59:53-04:00</published><updated> 2024-06-14T15:59:53-04:00</updated><title> 500 美元以下可以买到的最好的智能手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;来自 Google、Apple 和 Samsung 的手机，背景为彩色插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/t2Mje1exJnZyEZRBhf5hrBEQbvE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/67732462/226422_K_Radtke_budget_phone_buying_guide.1 3.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;如果您知道如何选择优先事项，现在您就可以花不到 500 美元购买一台出色的设备。&lt;/em>; |图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;你不可能以这个价格拥有一切，但你可以获得一部很棒的智能手机。无论您想要 iPhone、120Hz 屏幕还是防水，您都有选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21420196/best-budget-smartphone-便宜&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content>